17
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:28,357
[REN]
Rea!

18
00:02:34,863 --> 00:02:39,618
[REINHARD] Swallowed so quickly.
What a delightful surprise.

19
00:02:39,701 --> 00:02:41,828
Now that she's become
part of Isaak's world,

20
00:02:41,912 --> 00:02:44,289
