23
00:02:56,510 --> 00:02:59,054
No way. Not yet.

24
00:03:01,515 --> 00:03:03,809
Don't think
you've won, Heydrich!

25
00:03:15,112 --> 00:03:19,241
[REN] I've always wished that
I could make time stand still.

26
00:03:19,324 --> 00:03:22,452
That the ordinary life I
love would last forever.

27
00:03:24,162 --> 00:03:25,622
[REN]So I'll do it.

28
00:03:29,668 --> 00:03:31,670
[REN]
I'll take this moment.

29
00:03:33,130 --> 00:03:34,631
Creation!

30
00:03:36,258 --> 00:03:38,009
[REN]
I will stop time...

31
00:03:40,804 --> 00:03:44,182
[REN] ...and protect
the things I care about.

32
00:03:44,266 --> 00:03:48,186
<i>Eine Faust Ouvertüre</i> !

33
00:03:52,232 --> 00:03:57,195
♪

34
00:05:38,672 --> 00:05:43,134
My. You're quite fast.
But that's not enough.

35
00:05:43,218 --> 00:05:45,303
[REN grunts]

36
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,729
[REN shouts]

37
00:06:06,449 --> 00:06:07,659
[coughs]

38
00:06:27,178 --> 00:06:32,142
Well now. Perhaps I haven't
reached my full potency.

39
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:33,435
[REN grunts]

40
00:06:37,188 --> 00:06:40,150
[REINHARD] You see? I was
unable to avoid your attack.

41
00:06:40,233 --> 00:06:42,319
I promised you the
fight of your life,

42
00:06:42,402 --> 00:06:45,030
