deliver at this time.

43
00:06:46,489 --> 00:06:48,116
Und neither can you.

44
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:51,578
Therefore, we should
postpone our final battle.

45
00:06:51,661 --> 00:06:55,749
For now, I shall leave this in
the hands of one more suitable.

46
00:06:57,167 --> 00:07:00,962
Crush him, Machina.
Ja, und if you win,

47
00:07:01,046 --> 00:07:04,507
