unbound from Gladsheim.

48
00:07:08,053 --> 00:07:09,054
[MICHAEL grunts]

49
00:07:17,228 --> 00:07:18,438
Who are you?

50
00:07:18,521 --> 00:07:22,025
Let us begin,
<i>Mein Kamaraden</i> . To arms!

51
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:42,295
