a flair for the dramatic.

56
00:08:03,483 --> 00:08:05,402
[ELEONORE] Do you honestly
believe an exaggerated

57
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:08,154
performance like that
would deceive me?

58
00:08:08,238 --> 00:08:10,323
Tell me what you're
really planning.

59
00:08:10,407 --> 00:08:16,413
[KEI] Nothing... A personal
issue that doesn't concern you.

60
00:08:16,496 --> 00:08:19,499
[ELEONORE] Ah, so one that
has nothing to do with us?

61
00:08:19,582 --> 00:08:22,794
[KEI] Yes, and to answer
your previous question,

62
00:08:22,877 --> 00:08:26,172
I knew I couldn't fool you.

63
00:08:26,256 --> 00:08:28,174
After all...

64
00:08:28,258 --> 00:08:31,845
You didn't just give this to
me by some random coincidence.

65
00:08:31,928 --> 00:08:34,347
[ELEONORE] Tsk. So it
seems the eighth <i>swastika</i>

66
00:08:34,431 --> 00:08:38,643
was opened by the souls you had
collected up until this point.

67
00:08:38,727 --> 00:08:41,563
Und just before you
were going to shatter,

68
00:08:41,646 --> 00:08:43,773
