with a new relic,

69
00:08:43,857 --> 00:08:45,984
which is how you survived.

70
00:08:46,067 --> 00:08:48,069
A necessity.

71
00:08:48,153 --> 00:08:51,698
That thing only targets
you anyway, Sakurai.

72
00:08:53,158 --> 00:08:55,160
[ELEONORE] If its previous
holder was no more,

73
00:08:55,243 --> 00:08:58,371
und it had no new contract
to satisfy its hunger,

74
00:08:58,455 --> 00:09:01,791
