but to swallow you.

75
00:09:01,875 --> 00:09:03,793
What would normally
be considered a curse,

76
00:09:03,877 --> 00:09:07,297
seems to have been the only
thing that could save you.

77
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,924
You managed to use
it to your advantage.

78
00:09:10,008 --> 00:09:13,261
I must say, your resourcefulness
deserves praise.

79
00:09:13,344 --> 00:09:15,805
[KEI] You seem to know
a lot about this blade.

80
00:09:15,889 --> 00:09:20,143
Ja, of course I do. I was the
one who requested it be forged.

81
00:09:21,853 --> 00:09:24,814
[ELEONORE]
<i>Wewelsburg Longinus</i> .

82
00:09:24,898 --> 00:09:26,941
I'd like nothing more than
denounce such a thing

83
00:09:27,025 --> 00:09:30,070
as blasphemy. But Lord
Heydrich is a man who

84
00:09:30,153 --> 00:09:32,280
always gets what he wants.

85
00:09:32,363 --> 00:09:34,616
That's why I had to summon
your great grandfather

86
00:09:34,699 --> 00:09:37,619
from this country and bring
him to the <i>vaterland</i> .

87
00:09:37,702 --> 00:09:40,330
I reluctantly made him
an honorary Aryan

88
00:09:40,413 --> 00:09:43,291
und added him to our ranks.

89
00:09:43,374 --> 00:09:46,753
[KEI gasps]
So that was you?

90
00:09:46,836 --> 00:09:48,421
I'm sure you're quite grateful.

91
00:09:48,505 --> 00:09:52,050
Because of this, your family
attained its rare prestige.

92
00:09:53,802 --> 00:09:56,888
You think it's prestigious?
This burden we carry.

93
00:09:56,971 --> 00:10:00,100
The relic binding us to
the Black Round Table?

94
00:10:00,183 --> 00:10:01,684
What else could it be?

95
00:10:01,768 --> 00:10:08,817
[KEI exhales] I am grateful.
Much more than you realize.

96
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:11,486
You've given more
meaning to my fight.

97
00:10:16,658 --> 00:10:18,743
[KEI]
I can't expect to defeat you,

98
00:10:18,827 --> 00:10:21,538
unless I too take the next
step and become immortal.

99
00:10:21,621 --> 00:10:26,751
Although my skin may burn,
or my limbs fall off.

100
00:10:26,835 --> 00:10:28,545
Even if I'm reduced to
nothing but a head,

101
00:10:28,628 --> 00:10:34,008
