Tear your flesh with my fangs.

102
00:10:34,092 --> 00:10:38,888
I know... That joining them is
just another hopeless dream,

103
00:10:38,972 --> 00:10:40,849
because I don't deserve it.

104
00:10:44,102 --> 00:10:46,980
[KEI] I'd rather them
believe I was dead.

105
00:10:47,063 --> 00:10:51,317
Instead of waiting for me,
hoping I'll make it there.

106
00:10:53,570 --> 00:10:55,822
And you.

107
00:10:55,905 --> 00:10:57,991
To show you my gratitude...

108
00:11:01,494 --> 00:11:04,247
...I'll take you
to hell with me!

109
00:11:04,330 --> 00:11:05,540
Will you?

110
00:11:08,877 --> 00:11:12,046
[ELEONORE] Your kind is not
fit to live in Valhalla.

111
00:11:14,465 --> 00:11:15,925
[ELEONORE]
Your pathetic countrymen

112
00:11:16,009 --> 00:11:18,803
und their inferior genes are
completely incapable of becoming

113
00:11:18,887 --> 00:11:21,639
the golden Valkyries that
shall rain divine punishment

114
00:11:21,723 --> 00:11:23,474
upon this filthy world.

115
00:11:24,809 --> 00:11:27,854
[BOTH] After all these years,
you're still blind to the truth.

116
00:11:27,937 --> 00:11:30,273
Or do you just
refuse to admit it?

117
00:11:34,402 --> 00:11:36,070
[KEI, BEATRICE] Heydrich stole
something besides your

118
00:11:36,154 --> 00:11:40,491
heart back then. He took
away your sanity as well.

119
00:11:40,575 --> 00:11:42,202
It's more than loyalty.

120
00:11:42,285 --> 00:11:45,955
You pledged your life to him
for something else. For love.

121
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,582
