122
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,251
Are you done talking?

123
00:11:52,837 --> 00:11:56,591
I am, because my sword
will say the rest.

124
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:03,014
[KEI] As for you?
You'll cry out in defeat!

125
00:12:33,127 --> 00:12:34,504
[WOLFGANG grunts]

126
00:12:38,091 --> 00:12:40,218
[SHIROU grunts]

127
00:12:42,804 --> 00:12:44,305
[gasps]

128
00:12:50,937 --> 00:12:52,522
[WOLFGANG]
What's the matter?

129
00:12:52,605 --> 00:12:53,898
Are you done already?

130
00:12:53,982 --> 00:12:56,651
[SHIROU] Shut the hell up!
Just give me a second!

131
00:12:56,734 --> 00:13:00,446
[WOLFGANG] Okay. Why don't
we have a little chat?

132
00:13:00,530 --> 00:13:02,949
It will give you some time
for your wounds to heal.

133
00:13:03,032 --> 00:13:05,243
Or even look for an opening.

134
00:13:05,326 --> 00:13:07,453
You might come up
with a real strategy.

135
00:13:07,537 --> 00:13:08,913
[SHIROU]
Tsk!

136
00:13:08,997 --> 00:13:10,540
[WOLFGANG] Let me guess what
you're thinking right now.

137
00:13:10,623 --> 00:13:12,625
I bet you want to know why
I always choose to

138
00:13:12,709 --> 00:13:14,085
dodge your attacks.

139
00:13:14,168 --> 00:13:16,546
Especially at those times when
blocking them would prove

140
00:13:16,629 --> 00:13:18,256
to be more effective.

141
00:13:18,339 --> 00:13:22,468
