know the answer to that.

142
00:13:22,552 --> 00:13:24,971
Krawfft told me that many things
that I've done in my life have

143
00:13:25,054 --> 00:13:26,681
all come from my
overwhelming desire

144
00:13:26,764 --> 00:13:29,642
to never be touched by anyone.

145
00:13:29,726 --> 00:13:32,770
So it's not really a choice.
Just how I am.

146
00:13:32,854 --> 00:13:36,566
Ha! Probably because your old
man gave your ass a poke, right?

147
00:13:36,649 --> 00:13:38,151
[WOLFGANG]
How did you know?

148
00:13:38,234 --> 00:13:39,360
[SHIROU gasps]

149
00:13:40,862 --> 00:13:43,281
[WOLFGANG] It was the
family business, after all.

150
00:13:43,364 --> 00:13:46,075
Und if I wanted to eat,
I had to get to work.

151
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:48,745
