156
00:14:00,423 --> 00:14:03,426
und our clients would lavish
us with money und affection,

157
00:14:03,509 --> 00:14:06,596
To think of all the
stories I could tell you.

158
00:14:07,972 --> 00:14:11,059
[WOLFGANG] It's strange.
Looking back on it now,

159
00:14:11,142 --> 00:14:13,561
I can see how my relationship
with my mother suffered

160
00:14:13,644 --> 00:14:16,397
as I started to take
on more customers.

161
00:14:16,481 --> 00:14:19,567
