166
00:14:31,788 --> 00:14:33,873
because she was the one
who made me that way

167
00:14:33,956 --> 00:14:37,210
by cutting off my manhood and
giving me a woman's name.

168
00:14:39,587 --> 00:14:44,050
"You," she'd say.
"You're nobody."

169
00:14:44,133 --> 00:14:47,637
"There's nothing
special about you.

170
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:52,183
You're pitiful. Just a
stupid little boy.

171
00:14:52,266 --> 00:14:57,438
But I am a beautiful creature.
A true woman!

172
00:14:57,522 --> 00:15:00,733
