mommy issues, you psychopath!

185
00:15:46,696 --> 00:15:48,739
So put a sock in it already!

186
00:15:50,199 --> 00:15:52,577
Ha! You're too slow!

187
00:15:55,496 --> 00:15:58,040
Say hi to your parents.
Nighty‐night.

188
00:16:05,298 --> 00:16:06,841
[gasps]

189
00:16:09,802 --> 00:16:11,387
[WOLFGANG]
<i>Yetzirah</i> .

190
00:16:17,226 --> 00:16:20,146
[WOLFGANG]
<i>Lyngvi Vanargand</i> .

191
00:16:30,698 --> 00:16:31,991
[SHIROU]
