it took for you to finally lose

202
00:17:04,565 --> 00:17:06,108
your goddamn mind.

203
00:17:06,192 --> 00:17:09,070
Naw, it sounds like you
lost it a long time ago.

204
00:17:09,153 --> 00:17:12,782
Whaddaya say we wrap this up?
You can meet my girlfriend.

205
00:17:12,865 --> 00:17:14,450
