have to show you

209
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:33,302
how the sexes can work together
by kicking your sorry Nazi ass.

210
00:17:33,386 --> 00:17:36,514
[ERI sighs] I don't think
we're a realistic example

211
00:17:36,597 --> 00:17:39,100
