215
00:17:45,356 --> 00:17:47,650
but I've been the star of my
own movie for a while, now.

216
00:17:47,733 --> 00:17:50,152
You're a legend in
your own mind, huh?

217
00:17:51,362 --> 00:17:52,405
Time to man up.

218
00:17:52,488 --> 00:17:54,073
Bring it on, kiddo!

219
00:17:57,368 --> 00:17:58,953
Shut your mouth!

220
00:18:01,622 --> 00:18:05,585
I am an immortal
<i>einherjar</i> of Valhalla!

221
00:18:05,668 --> 00:18:10,673
