now may fall to dust!

230
00:19:00,598 --> 00:19:04,602
Farewell, proud radiant,
godly race!

231
00:19:04,685 --> 00:19:07,188
<i>Briah</i> !

232
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:11,525
Come beast of the Abyss.
<i>Niffle</i> ‐ <i>haym</i> Fenris Wolf!

233
00:19:14,403 --> 00:19:15,738
