[REN] Old friend?
I don't know who you are!

241
00:19:52,566 --> 00:19:56,654
[MICHAEL] I see. So you don't
remember my former name?

242
00:19:56,737 --> 00:19:57,738
[REN gasps]

243
00:20:00,074 --> 00:20:02,451
[MICHAEL] I've forgotten
what my true name was.

244
00:20:02,535 --> 00:20:04,453
It died, but I live.

245
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:08,958
[gasps]

246
00:20:11,001 --> 00:20:12,920
[MICHAEL]
You look at me with disgust,

247
00:20:13,003 --> 00:20:16,215
but we're both the
playthings of Karl Krafft.

248
00:20:16,298 --> 00:20:19,343
We're much more alike
than you want to admit.

249
00:20:27,101 --> 00:20:29,854
[MICHAEL] We both went
onto the battlefield.

250
00:20:29,937 --> 00:20:33,566
We both fought.
Und we both died.

251
00:20:35,109 --> 00:20:36,902
[REN grunts]

252
00:20:36,986 --> 00:20:40,156
[MICHAEL]
So... why are we here now?

253
00:20:40,239 --> 00:20:42,366
Why can we not rest in peace?

254
00:20:44,493 --> 00:20:48,205
We both came back to life
inside Lord Heydrich's castle.

255
00:20:48,289 --> 00:20:50,791
But we never asked for that!

256
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:54,044
Tell me what you wish for
in the life you have now.

257
00:20:55,463 --> 00:20:56,547
[REN shouts]

258
00:20:56,630 --> 00:21:00,843
[MICHAEL]
My wish... My wish is for death.

259
00:21:00,926 --> 00:21:03,804
The last thing stolen from me.

260
00:21:03,888 --> 00:21:04,847
[REN gasps]

261
00:21:06,432 --> 00:21:11,103
You und I are comrades. So let's
go out as brothers in arms.

262
00:21:11,187 --> 00:21:12,396
[REN gasps]

263
00:21:13,981 --> 00:21:16,317
The battle today
will grant my wish.

264
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:19,528
You will release me from
this prison of existence.

265
00:21:21,864 --> 00:21:25,326
Let's go together.
Come with me to Valhalla!

266
00:21:35,211 --> 00:21:42,384
Marie... Hear me...
I swear... I'll protect you.

267
00:21:42,468 --> 00:21:46,138
For this world. And the one
we can create together.

268
00:21:46,222 --> 00:21:47,848
For our future.

269
00:21:50,059 --> 00:21:51,644
<i>Oui</i> .

270
00:21:51,727 --> 00:21:54,313
That's the same reason why
I want to protect you too,

271
00:21:54,396 --> 00:21:56,148
<i>mon chérie</i> .

272
00:21:56,232 --> 00:21:59,985
Our future of loving.
One that's filled with laughter.

273
00:22:00,069 --> 00:22:03,781
Where we can hold each
other and never let go.

274
00:22:03,864 --> 00:22:05,574
I'll take these
feelings and shield you

275
00:22:05,658 --> 00:22:07,993
from every pain and sorrow.

276
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:13,958
I will embrace this entire
world and care for it as my own.

277
00:22:18,170 --> 00:22:23,133
♪

